nodes.text: Lady Wylla was a female Alderaanian noble. At some point during galactic history, Wylla hired a group of agents to purchase some nerf steaks from Davengatt's Double-Zed Nerf Ranch on the planet Engebo V. She provided the agents with a Corellian freighter and insisted that they deliver the steaks to her within three days of picking them up, so as to preserve the steaks' freshness.
